Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; NoteMark COM Add-In - Unregistration
; Removes all NoteMark.AddIn entries from OneNote AddIns registry keys

; ===== Remove OneNote Add-In Registration (HKCU) =====
[-HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Office\OneNote\AddIns\NoteMark.AddIn]

; ===== Remove OneNote Add-In Registration (HKLM) =====
[-HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Microsoft\Office\OneNote\AddIns\NoteMark.AddIn]
